      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model with Ti-6Al-4V properties (E = 114 GPa, ν = 0.34) is well-established for sub-yield compression-bending of pedicle screw constructs. Geometry imported directly from DePuy Synthes production CAD files. UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate modeled as bilinear elastic-plastic consistent with published material characterization data."
    },
