      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from lot-specific coupon testing or peer-reviewed literature with stated uncertainty bounds; geometric inputs traceable to metrology reports.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus and yield strength taken from lot-specific tensile coupon data (n=5 coupons, CV < 2%). UHMWPE block properties from published ASTM D638 characterization. Rod and screw geometry verified against CMM measurement reports with tolerances within ±0.05 mm. Input uncertainty propagated through the validation metric."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "N ≥ 10 constructs tested; samples drawn from production lots; dimensional inspection confirms geometric conformance.",
      "rationale": "N=11 constructs tested across two independent laboratories (n=6 Lab A, n=5 Lab B). All constructs assembled from production-released components. Pre-test CMM inspection confirmed all critical dimensions within drawing tolerances. Sample size exceeds the minimum threshold for Medium assurance level."
